Third-party content embedded in this repository:

- `flows.json` contains nodes imported from
  https://github.com/VU3ESV/LP-700-Server (examples/node-red/
  lp700-websocket-flow.json) — that upstream repository is unlicensed at
  the time of import. Those nodes retain whatever terms VU3ESV chooses to
  apply; the MIT license above covers only original VU2CPL contributions.
- Historical references to KD4Z's "LP Dice and Slice" Node-RED flow appear
  in commit history; the parser itself was removed in commit c449c49.
- External services consumed at runtime (Open-Meteo, NOAA SWPC, Club Log,
  prop.kc2g.com, RBN sm7iun calibration, Tasmota, FlexRadio TCP API) are
  used as clients only; their data and APIs are governed by the respective
  service terms.
